{"tid":997670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人細個睇過老夫子","createTime":"2019-01-27T10:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T10:50:19.000Z","uid":201091,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bd19d70780295ee798776f8af87994c620fee798","tid":997670,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"我細個個陣<br />\n家境十分貧窮<br />\n但父母依然每兩個禮拜<br />\n俾二十蚊我買老夫子<br />\n所以我非常珍惜本老夫子<br />\n無論食野 温書 <br />\n甚至係去廁所都揸住本老夫子<br />\n當我再大個d之後<br />\n我終於知道二十蚊其實好多<br />\n從此我就冇再要求買老夫子<br />\n當唔再買同睇老夫子<br />\n我就知童年已過去"},{"pid":"5ced3ef6612c4956ff50243c6a3208a4b04c21e9","tid":997670,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"我細個都係睇老夫子<br />\n但我唔會叫屋企人買<br />\n我會喺ok店打書釘<br />\n一係就問朋友借<br />\n係咪好狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afbf238329ce0755841f2caf690fabaa28fb09b","tid":997670,"uid":40470,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"老夫子唔同期數都好<br />\n<br />\n好似內容成日重複？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7614bd84050842b22b61637e8ff1cdde2198af15","tid":997670,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ced3ef6612c4956ff50243c6a3208a4b04c21e9","tid":997670,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"我細個都係睇老夫子<br />\n但我唔會叫屋企人買<br />\n我會喺ok店打書釘<br />\n一係就問朋友借<br />\n係咪好狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"我細個主要幫襯報紙檔<br />\n所以冇得打書釘"},{"pid":"3eb56c15158cb8526b16a770ebc7067c5ecfb33e","tid":997670,"uid":3600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"依家新一代已經無咩人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e5724abf120ee7f017c22f7a6e9bfbbc9486bb","tid":997670,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5